	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really want to change the refresh speed of Nijuu to 120hz. Has anyone done it with their sound engine and what's best practice (i.e. I know calling the refresh routine twice in the NMI is NOT the way to go <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> )

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

